{"sqlDbType":"server","Sql":"SELECT  a1.itemmasterid, a1.itemid AS itemid, a2.mgroupname AS itemgroup, a1.valmethod, a3.unitid AS priunit, a1.scf AS sellingcf, a4.subgroupid AS subgroup ,s.tqty
FROM itemmaster a1,igbasic a2,  unitmast a3 ,igdetail a4, stockvalue s,locdetails l
WHERE a1.maingroup = a2.igbasicid
AND a1.priunit=a3.unitmastid
AND a1.subgroup=a4.igdetailid AND s.fslocid=l.locdetailsid AND s.mapname='ltrf3 (+)' AND s.itemid=a1.itemmasterid AND l.locdetailsid=:fslocid
AND (a2.mgroupname  = 'FIELD I/P' OR  a2.mgroupname  = 'FIELD O/P') ORDER BY a1.itemid","key":"itemid","value":"itemmasterid"}

{"sqlDbType":"server","Sql":"SELECT DISTINCT b.branchmastid,b.branchname FROM branchmast b,empmaster e\nWHERE e.branchid = b.branchmastid AND e.mobno = :mobileno\nORDER BY 2","key":"branchname","value":"branchmastid"}

{"sqlDbType":"server","Sql":"SELECT a.amasterid,a.areaname,a.areasid  FROM amaster a,empmaster e,emparea ea\nWHERE e.empmasterid = ea.empmasterid AND ea.emparea1 = a.amasterid  AND ea.activeyn = 'YES' \nAND e.mobno= :mobileno","key":"areaname","value":"amasterid"}

{"sqlDbType":"server","Sql":"SELECT  a1.empmasterid, a1.employee_name, a3.areaname AS emparea, a1.empdept
FROM empmaster a1, emparea a2, amaster a3
WHERE a1.empmasterid=a2.empmasterid  
AND a2.emparea1=a3.amasterid 
AND a3.areaname = :areaname AND a1.mobno=:mobileno AND a1.empdept = 'FIELD STAFF' AND a2.activeyn = 'YES'
ORDER BY a1.employee_name","key":"employee_name","value":"empmasterid"}

{"sqlDbType":"server","Sql":"SELECT l.locdetailsid, l.locid,l.locationtype  FROM locdetails l,branchmast b WHERE l.branchid=b.branchmastid AND l.locationtype='FIELD-STAFF' AND b.branchid=:branchid AND l.locid=:emplocid","key":"locid","value":"locdetailsid"}
{"sqlDbType":"client","Sql":"select f.sfinyr from finyrsplit f\nwhere sysdate() between f.sfinyrst and f.sfinyred","key":"sfinyr","value":"sfinyr"}

{"sqlDbType":"server","Sql":"SELECT a1.vmasterid, a1.villagename, a2.areaname FROM vmaster a1, amaster a2,empmaster e ,emparea ea  
WHERE a1.areaname = a2.amasterid AND e.empmasterid = ea.empmasterid AND ea.emparea1 = a2.amasterid AND ea.activeyn = 'YES' 
AND e.mobno = :mobileno
ORDER BY 2","key":"villagename","value":"vmasterid"}

{"sqlDbType":"server","Sql":"SELECT DISTINCT cropscheme FROM cropmaster c,igdetail ig \nWHERE c.crop = ig.igdetailid AND ig.subgroup = :cropname AND c.is_cancelled = 'F'\nORDER BY 1","key":"cropscheme","value":"cropscheme"}
